---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact - SkillStart Jobs" description="Get in touch with SkillStart Jobs for support, feedback, partnerships, and reporting issues.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumbs"><a href="/">Home</a> / Contact</div>
      <h1>We&rsquo;d Love to Hear From You</h1>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="content-card">
        <p>Welcome to the Contact Page of SkillStart Jobs. We value feedback, questions, and suggestions from our visitors.</p>
        <p>Whether you need help, want to report an issue, suggest improvements, or contact us regarding business inquiries, feel free to reach out.</p>

        <h2>How We Can Help</h2>
        <p>You may contact us for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>General questions about the website</li>
          <li>Reporting incorrect job information</li>
          <li>Broken links or technical issues</li>
          <li>Suggestions to improve user experience</li>
          <li>Advertising or partnership inquiries</li>
          <li>Copyright / DMCA concerns</li>
          <li>Privacy-related questions</li>
          <li>Content correction requests</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Important Note About Job Applications</h2>
        <p>SkillStart Jobs is an informational platform and does not directly hire candidates for most listed opportunities.</p>
        <p>Please do not send job applications or CVs to our contact email unless a specific listing asks for it.</p>
        <p>For jobs, always apply through the method mentioned on the relevant job page.</p>

        <h2>Response Time</h2>
        <p>We aim to respond to genuine inquiries within a reasonable time, usually within 24 to 72 business hours, depending on message volume.</p>

        <h2>Contact Methods</h2>
        <h3>Email Support</h3>
        <p>Use your official support email:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:support@skillstartjobs.online">support@skillstartjobs.online</a></p>

        <h3>Business / Advertising</h3>
        <p>For promotions, collaborations, or advertising opportunities:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:business@skillstartjobs.online">business@skillstartjobs.online</a></p>

        <h3>Copyright / DMCA</h3>
        <p>For copyright concerns:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:dmca@skillstartjobs.online">dmca@skillstartjobs.online</a></p>

        <h2>Before Contacting Us</h2>
        <p>For faster support, please include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Reason for contacting us</li>
          <li>Relevant page URL (if reporting an issue)</li>
          <li>Clear explanation of the problem</li>
          <li>Screenshot if helpful</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Report Fake or Suspicious Jobs</h2>
        <p>If you notice any suspicious listing, scam attempt, misleading information, or fake recruiter behavior, please contact us immediately.</p>
        <p>Your report helps protect other users.</p>

        <h2>Suggestions Welcome</h2>
        <p>We are continuously improving SkillStart Jobs. If you have ideas for better features, categories, or content, we&rsquo;d love to hear them.</p>

        <h2>Our Goal</h2>
        <p>Our goal is to create a helpful platform for job seekers across Pakistan by improving access to clear job information and practical career guidance.</p>

        <h2>Thank You</h2>
        <p>Thank you for visiting SkillStart Jobs and being part of our growing community.</p>

        <h2>Quick Message Form</h2>
        <form data-contact-form novalidate>
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" class="field" type="text" required />

          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" class="field" type="email" required />

          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>

          <p><button class="btn-primary" type="submit">Send Message</button></p>
          <p data-contact-status aria-live="polite"></p>
        </form>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>


